    "TitleKey": "DeadSaints_RecoverCargo_Medium_Title",
    "Description": "You got a ship and <EM4>a heavy-duty tractor beam</EM4>? Good. I\u2019ve got work for you.\n\nDon\u2019t know how they knew we were coming, but one of my haulers got jumped over at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>. The pilot\u2019s gone silent so I assume they\u2019ve been ghosted, but the cargo tracker is stationary for now.\n\nExpect the bastards who took out my pilot to still be around, so bring backup. Get the cargo and get out, don\u2019t need to risk anymore good haulers on this mess.\n\nGet the goods to the freight elevator to <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4> and I\u2019ll send your payment.\n\n-Twitch",
    "DescriptionKey": "DeadSaints_RecoverCargo_Medium_Description",
    "DisplayDescription": "You got a ship and <EM4>a heavy-duty tractor beam</EM4>? Good. I\u2019ve got work for you.\n\nDon\u2019t know how they knew we were coming, but one of my haulers got jumped over at <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4>. The pilot\u2019s gone silent so I assume they\u2019ve been ghosted, but the cargo tracker is stationary for now.\n\nExpect the bastards who took out my pilot to still be around, so bring backup. Get the cargo and get out, don\u2019t need to risk anymore good haulers on this mess.\n\nGet the goods to the freight elevator to <EM4>[Destination|Address]</EM4> and I\u2019ll send your payment.\n\n-Twitch",
